**Dutch National Flag — 3 pointers:**

```java
// Sort Colors: 0=red, 1=white, 2=blue
void sortColors(int[] nums) {
    int low=0, mid=0, high=nums.length-1;
    while (mid <= high) {
        if (nums[mid] == 0) {      // red: move to front
            swap(nums, low++, mid++);
        } else if (nums[mid] == 1) { // white: correct position
            mid++;
        } else {                   // blue: move to end
            swap(nums, mid, high--);
            // Note: don't increment mid — swapped element needs checking
        }
    }
}
// O(n) time, O(1) space — one pass, three regions:
// [0..low-1] = all 0s (red)
// [low..mid-1] = all 1s (white)
// [high+1..n-1] = all 2s (blue)
// [mid..high] = unexplored
```
